	<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">R/Editors</h1>
	<div id="bodyContent">
		<div id="siteSub">From QERM Wiki</div>
		<div id="contentSub"></div>
		<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>
		<!-- start content -->
<p>There are tons of text editors available and many of them have modes for highlighting R syntax. This page is a place to list editors that contributors to this wiki have used and perhaps make notes about how to get them to work for R.
</p><p>Wikipedia has a good deal of information on costs, platforms, features <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Comparison_of_text_editors" class="external text" rel="nofollow">here</a>.
</p>
